AFN BULLBAR TO SUIT VOLKSWAGEN AMAROK (2010+)

AFN bullbar to suit Volkswagen Amarok (2010+) available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

The pictured bullbar features;

  • Full Bumper Replacement
  • Rated Recovery Points
  • Dual Antenna Tabs
  • Winch Compatible
  • Hi-Lift Jack Points
  • Fog/Indicator Light Assemblies
  • Sensor brackets

PLEASE NOTE: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order. 

CLICK HERE to view the range of products available for your VW Amarok!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
